2482:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *  The function discharge available external capacitors.
2483:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *
2484:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** * \details
2485:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *  The function discharge available external capacitors by connection them
2486:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *  to GND using STRONG GPIO drive mode. Additionaly, the function disconnects
2487:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *  the capacitors from analog mux buses if connected.
