2489:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *  and supposes that all the capacitors belong to a single device port.
2490:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *
2491:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *******************************************************************************/
